✨ Hero \u0026 CTA\\nA bold headline with sub-text and a clear call-to-action to capture attention right away.\\n\\n📊 Product Features\\nFeature blocks with supporting visuals/screenshots to highlight scheduling, analytics, and collaboration.\\n\\n🤝 Social Proof \u0026 Integrations\\nLogos, testimonials, and tool integrations that add trust and show compatibility.\\n\\n💵 Pricing Plans\\nSimple, tiered pricing cards that help users compare and choose easily.\\n\\n❓ FAQ \u0026 Footer\\nAnswers to common questions and a clean footer to wrap up the page.\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://gvsmhepiuiax2e6y.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/templates/assets/CleanShot%202025-09-15%20at%2008.35.08%402x-yc6PzoSg51q5wlOnRqRQUrAlC2Kyaq.png\",\"title\":\"Brillance SaaS Landing Page\",\"publishedToCommunity\":\"approved\",\"templateCanonId\":\"zdiN8dHwaaT\",\"templateVersionId\":\"1cXyD5qxnJS\",\"uses\":12822,\"authorId\":\"Xt8wqxzkatVdL270RPPaEkHw\",\"isTeamTemplate\":false,\"likeCount\":1920,\"vercelDeploymentUrl\":null,\"ownerId\":\"Xt8wqxzkatVdL270RPPaEkHw\",\"createdAt\":\"2025-09-15T02:59:48.798Z\",\"category\":\"landing-pages\",\"tags\":[\"saas\",\"landing-page\",\"minimal\"]},\"className\":\"\",\"withAvatar\":true}],[\"$\",\"$Lcc\",\"JUFK37Esjlj-2\",{\"index\":2,\"showStatus\":false,\"template\":{\"blockId\":\"b_qH8mHOVfAEd\",\"description\":\"Modern sleek 3D slideshow that showcases a photo gallery created with v0, react three fiber, webgl\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://gvsmhepiuiax2e6y.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/templates/assets/3d-gallery-thumb-kwJA6jZ54xtOk4Rfilti7xqp8Pc37I.jpg\",\"title\":\"3D Gallery Photography Template\",\"publishedToCommunity\":\"approved\",\"templateCanonId\":\"JUFK37Esjlj\",\"templateVersionId\":\"p6zHw9Vd9kv\",\"uses\":2983,\"authorId\":\"eIM9a1GGLbVpKzANsjrpwRF6\",\"isTeamTemplate\":false,\"likeCount\":776,\"vercelDeploymentUrl\":null,\"ownerId\":\"eIM9a1GGLbVpKzANsjrpwRF6\",\"createdAt\":\"2025-09-24T17:07:57.620Z\",\"category\":\"animations\",\"tags\":[\"modern\",\"design\",\"gallery\",\"minimal\",\"3d\",\"webgl\"]},\"className\":\"\",\"withAvatar\":true}],[\"$\",\"$Lcc\",\"LHv4frpA7Us-3\",{\"index\":3,\"showStatus\":false,\"template\":{\"blockId\":\"b_0NxSgg7fz8b\",\"description\":\"Optimus empowers teams to build, deploy, and scale applications with unprecedented velocity on a global infrastructure. Streamline your workflow from connecting tools to shipping production-ready code, leveraging AI-native capabilities and enterprise-grade security. This platform offers a seamless developer experience with an intuitive SDK, real-time collaboration, and instant deployments.\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://gvsmhepiuiax2e6y.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/templates/assets/ezgif-464bbe623ade3f56-nNnxi4IMwxHh8nXLULPHLdglqOwBsk.webp\",\"title\":\"Optimus - The AI platform to build and ship\",\"publishedToCommunity\":\"approved\",\"templateCanonId\":\"LHv4frpA7Us\",\"templateVersionId\":\"u42JoxEBY5s\",\"uses\":3041,\"authorId\":\"sgeDKOyvY41XAreXMDwcFJSG\",\"isTeamTemplate\":false,\"likeCount\":649,\"vercelDeploymentUrl\":\"https://v0-optimus-delta.vercel.app\",\"ownerId\":\"sgeDKOyvY41XAreXMDwcFJSG\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-07T17:59:41.463Z\",\"category\":\"landing-pages\",\"tags\":[\"modern\",\"light\",\"website\",\"minimal\",\"bold\",\"animation\",\"landing-page\",\"ai\",\"shaders\",\"particles\"]},\"className\":\"\",\"withAvatar\":true}],\"$Lcd\",\"$Lce\",\"$Lcf\",\"$Ld0\",\"$Ld1\",\"$Ld2\",\"$Ld3\",\"$Ld4\",\"$Ld5\",\"$Ld6\",\"$Ld7\",\"$Ld8\",\"$Ld9\",\"$Lda\",\"$Ldb\",\"$Ldc\",\"$Ldd\",\"$Lde\",\"$Ldf\",\"$Le0\",\"$Le1\",\"$Le2\",\"$Le3\",\"$Le4\",\"$Le5\",\"$Le6\",\"$Le7\",\"$Le8\",\"$Le9\",\"$Lea\",\"$Leb\",\"$Lec\",\"$Led\",\"$Lee\",\"$Lef\",\"$Lf0\",\"$Lf1\",\"$Lf2\",\"$Lf3\",\"$Lf4\",\"$Lf5\",\"$Lf6\",\"$Lf7\",\"$Lf8\",\"$Lf9\",\"$Lfa\"]}]}]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"cd:[\"$\",\"$Lcc\",\"7YygHkO1oj4-4\",{\"index\":4,\"showStatus\":false,\"template\":{\"blockId\":\"b_OC1OyIfXKsu\",\"description\":\"An open-source AI image and video generation app built with Next.js, AI SDK, and xAI's Grok models via Vercel AI Gateway.\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://gvsmhepiuiax2e6y.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/templates/assets/slack-imgs-Kab3HFsD4fOkimOeOquiwfbgUy9nql.png\",\"title\":\"Grok Creative Studio\",\"publishedToCommunity\":\"approved\",\"templateCanonId\":\"7YygHkO1oj4\",\"templateVersionId\":\"WAbvVGgbR3k\",\"uses\":787,\"authorId\":\"a8wLiIgtTLckwJGixqXnytT3\",\"isTeamTemplate\":false,\"likeCount\":93,\"vercelDeploymentUrl\":\"https://v0-grokcreativestudiotemplate-5i.vercel.app\",\"ownerId\":\"a8wLiIgtTLckwJGixqXnytT3\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-02-24T13:48:31.618Z\",\"category\":\"ai\",\"tags\":[\"grok\",\"xai\",\"template\",\"media\",\"generation\",\"aisdk\"]},\"className\":\"\",\"withAvatar\":true}]\nce:[\"$\",\"$Lcc\",\"99MAOQptgL3-5\",{\"index\":5,\"showStatus\":false,\"template\":{\"blockId\":\"b_I77HHnrYRj1\",\"description\":null,\"imageUrl\":\"https://gvsmhepiuiax2e6y.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/templates/assets/Slide%2016_9%20-%205-54TEBSAuw3n3WPJPGdbFeOYE01RQRq.png\",\"title\":\"Globe To Map Transform\",\"publishedToCommunity\":\"approved\",\"templateCanonId\":\"99MAOQptgL3\",\"templateVersionId\":\"wNOrEYTQRQ7\",\"uses\":1916,\"authorId\":\"YdmoFpBLmXOqQX0oEPAJvCPr\",\"isTeamTemplate\":false,\"likeCount\":578,\"vercelDeploymentUrl\":null,\"ownerId\":\"YdmoFpBLmXOqQX0oEPAJvCPr\",\"createdAt\":\"2025-11-18T03:17:20.751Z\",\"category\":\"components\",\"tags\":[\"globe\",\"map\",\"3d\",\"2d\",\"wireframe\",\"transform\",\"d3js\",\"dataviz\"]},\"className\":\"\",\"withAvatar\":true}]\ncf:[\"$\",\"$Lcc\",\"E2PMKQo5S11-6\",{\"index\":6,\"showStatus\":false,\"template\":{\"blockId\":\"b_thsjr9F0NpQ\",\"description\":\"A minimal Next.js app demonstrating how to implement Sign in with Vercel authentication.\\n\\nThis template shows how to:\\n- Authenticate users with their Vercel account\\n- Exchange authorization codes for tokens\\n- Access basic profile information\\n- Configure environment variables\\n\\nIdeal for developers who want to:\\n- Add Vercel identity to their app\\n- Explore the Sign in with Vercel flow\\n- Bootstrap OAuth integration without starting from scratch\\n\\nIncludes a working example UI and a step-by-step README to get up and running quickly.\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://gvsmhepiuiax2e6y.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/templates/assets/sign%20in%20with%20vercel%20button-74DxeiMUaeE81jcTn9EidcnHp6kl1d.png\",\"title\":\"Sign in with Vercel\",\"publishedToCommunity\":\"approved\",\"templateCanonId\":\"E2PMKQo5S11\",\"templateVersionId\":\"3O67tiw5UAc\",\"uses\":20,\"authorId\":\"XLrCnEgbKhsHyfbiNR7E849p\",\"isTeamTemplate\":false,\"likeCount\":9,\"vercelDeploymentUrl\":\"https://v0-sign-in-with-vercel-template.vercel.app\",\"ownerId\":\"XLrCnEgbKhsHyfbiNR7E849p\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-02-06T10:29:49.948Z\",\"category\":\"login-and-sign-up\",\"tags\":[\"login\",\"oauth\"]},\"className\":\"hidden\",\"withAvatar\":true}]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"d0:[\"$\",\"$Lcc\",\"XQxxv76lK5w-7\",{\"index\":7,\"showStatus\":false,\"template\":{\"blockId\":\"b_e5SmnNUpCmm\",\"description\":\"I built this template in v0 to make it easy to customize and feel good to use. It’s simple, clean, and responds fast when you change things. \\n\\nSections in this template: Hero, Features, Pricing, Testimonials, Call to Action, Footer\\n\\nHere’s what’s in it:\\n\\n• Change the whole theme with a one message\\nYou can switch from light to dark or anything else just by typing a prompt. No settings panel, no config files.\\n\\n• Smooth, natural animations\\n Stuff fades in, slides in, or shifts in ways that feel right. Nothing jerky or overdone.\\n\\n• Clean layout and spacing\\nEverything is placed with breathing room. No clutter. It feels calm.\\n\\n• Mobile-ready without effort\\nIt looks great on phones and tablets out of the box.\\n\\n• Quick to start with, easy to edit\\nYou can make it your own in minutes. And it doesn’t fall apart when you do.\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://gvsmhepiuiax2e6y.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/templates/screenshots/XQxxv76lK5w-NSlaJ9vWreXbB4Bo77QQKwRQDPE8bP.jpg\",\"title\":\"Pointer AI landing page\",\"publishedToCommunity\":\"approved\",\"templateCanonId\":\"XQxxv76lK5w\",\"templateVersionId\":\"lp8KdvVDEDV\",\"uses\":19470,\"authorId\":\"Xt8wqxzkatVdL270RPPaEkHw\",\"isTeamTemplate\":false,\"likeCount\":1736,\"vercelDeploymentUrl\":null,\"ownerId\":\"Xt8wqxzkatVdL270RPPaEkHw\",\"createdAt\":\"2025-07-30T09:18:57.284Z\",\"category\":\"landing-pages\",\"tags\":[]},\"className\":\"hidden\",\"withAvatar\":true}]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"d1:[\"$\",\"$Lcc\",\"b7GDYVxuoGC-8\",{\"index\":8,\"showStatus\":false,\"template\":{\"blockId\":\"b_anFUtsGky30\",\"description\":\"Dashboard – M.O.N.K.Y is a JOYCO-made internal tool designed for high-speed teams and technical operators. Built with rebels in mind, it combines clean structure with punchy visuals and a dead-simple workflow. Everything you need to move fast—and look good doing it.\\n\\n• Integrated chat\\n• Custom design system\\n• Multi-view layout\\n• Collapsible sidebar and top bar\\n• Dark mode by default\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://gvsmhepiuiax2e6y.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/templates/assets/1-yP0cCw1D2jiVbM5P2HG6Og8KXfhbY6.png\",\"title\":\"Dashboard – M.O.N.K.Y\",\"publishedToCommunity\":\"approved\",\"templateCanonId\":\"b7GDYVxuoGC\",\"templateVersionId\":\"v49hFr91MFR\",\"uses\":10604,\"authorId\":\"ZNJvi2SET9uoaJJF75wa6XiN\",\"isTeamTemplate\":false,\"likeCount\":1170,\"vercelDeploymentUrl\":null,\"ownerId\":\"ZNJvi2SET9uoaJJF75wa6XiN\",\"createdAt\":\"2025-08-20T23:59:13.248Z\",\"category\":\"dashboards\",\"tags\":[\"dashboard\",\"tech\",\"internal\",\"chat\",\"system\"]},\"className\":\"hidden\",\"withAvatar\":true}]\nfb:T79e,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"An immersive digital experience for professional motocross rider Lorenzo Cardoso, built with the latest web technologies. Inspired by the Lando Norris website.\n\nThis project is a high-performance landing page that combines bold design with sophisticated interactions, creating a unique visual narrative about the athlete's journey and personality. Developed with Next.js 16, React 19, Framer Motion, Tailwind CSS v4, and Canvas API, the application explores the limits of the modern web to deliver fluid animations and memorable interactive experiences.\n\nThis architecture creates a \"progressive reveal\" effect inspired by premium Lando Norris website, using framer-motion to control scale, opacity, and positioning with millimeter precision.\n\n🛠 Innovative Interactions\n\n- Interactive Portrait (Hero): WebGL liquid effect with THREE.js that reveals textured layers on mouseover, with persistent trail and gradual decay\n- Interactive Clean: Simulation of \"cleaning\" the rider's mud using Canvas 2D API, with jagged brush mask and trail that persists for 45 seconds before disappearing\n- Adaptive Header: Intelligent logo color change based on `IntersectionObserver`, ensuring readability on light and dark backgrounds\n\n⚡ Performance and Technical Stack\n\n- Next.js 16 (App Router, React Server Components, caching with `cacheLife`)\n- React 19.2 (including `useEffectEvent` and `\u003cActivity\u003e` for state optimization)\n- Framer Motion 11 (orchestration of complex animations with `AnimatePresence`) and `motion.div`)\n- Canvas API + WebGL (THREE.js) (mask and real-time rendering effects)\n- Tailwind CSS v4 (inline token design system, no `tailwind.config.js`)\n- TypeScript (full type-safety)\n\nThis project demonstrates how to combine advanced front-end engineering with experimental design to create digital experiences that transcend the conventional, ideal for athlete portfolios, premium brands, or products that require impactful visual narratives."])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"d2:[\"$\",\"$Lcc\",\"jz21jJIFr0i-9\",{\"index\":9,\"showStatus\":false,\"template\":{\"blockId\":\"